Summary:        Real-time software synthesizer
Name:           zynaddsubfx
Version:        3.0.6
Release:        9%{?dist}
# Source is a collective work, distributed by
# Automatically converted from old format: GPLv2 and GPLv2+ - review is highly recommended.
